---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Install BridgeAIChat Agent">
  <section class="card">
    <div class="eyebrow">Install</div>
    <h1>Agent devices</h1>
    <p>Pick the release archive that matches your device architecture, then configure the gateway URL over Tailscale.</p>
    <pre>chmod +x ./bridge-agent
cp agent.yaml.example agent.yaml
./bridge-agent -config ./agent.yaml</pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
